216
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:06,250
and hold a press conference here.

217
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:07,640
Let them have a look.

218
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,860
Look at your working environment

219
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:11,190
and your achievements.

220
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,470
See what the real Bolamula

221
00:11:12,470 --> 00:11:13,330
is like.

222
00:11:14,860 --> 00:11:15,430
There is

223
00:11:15,460 --> 00:11:16,660
nothing more persuasive

224
00:11:16,660 --> 00:11:17,140
than bloody facts

225
00:11:17,140 --> 00:11:18,330
and the price paid.

226
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,040
Through this,

227
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:23,440
we can let more people see,

228
00:11:23,610 --> 00:11:24,230
hear,

229
00:11:24,330 --> 00:11:25,960
and truly understand

230
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,180
the importance of establishing

231
00:11:27,180 --> 00:11:28,180
a nature reserve.

232
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:32,200
Great idea.

233
00:11:33,060 --> 00:11:34,870
Relying solely on our own strength

234
00:11:34,870 --> 00:11:36,330
is just a drop in the ocean.

235
00:11:38,090 --> 00:11:39,840
The establishment of the nature reserve

236
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,440
can't be delayed any longer.

237
00:11:42,150 --> 00:11:42,820
I will definitely

238
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:44,620
finish the report on the reserve

239
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:47,080
before the press conference is held.

240
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:47,590
Okay.

241
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:51,470
What about getting the word out?

242
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,600
Let me have a drink first.

243
00:11:54,250 --> 00:11:56,050
What about getting the word out?

244
00:11:56,970 --> 00:11:57,640
How's that?

245
00:11:58,630 --> 00:11:59,890
I'm quite good, right?

246
00:12:00,110 --> 00:12:00,800
Bai Ju.

247
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:05,140
Looking for a beating again?

248
00:12:05,140 --> 00:12:05,700
No, no, not at all.

249
00:12:05,700 --> 00:12:06,560
I'll continue.

250
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:10,240
Getting the word out.

251
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:13,570
We must scientifically
analyze the situation,

252
00:12:13,570 --> 00:12:15,370
precisely grasp the key points,

253
00:12:15,850 --> 00:12:18,050
and fully focus on economic operations

254
00:12:18,160 --> 00:12:20,500
and tasks such as project construction.

255
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:25,240
The establishment of the development zone
is proceeding in an orderly manner.

256
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,000
In summary,

257
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:27,600
the economic topic

258
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,560
is still

259
00:12:28,590 --> 00:12:30,120
the priority

260
00:12:30,140 --> 00:12:31,580
among the upcoming operations.

261
00:12:31,580 --> 00:12:32,220
Here,

262
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:34,290
I extend a sincere invitation

263
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,520
to enterprises nationwide

264
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:37,590
and people from all walks of life.

265
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:39,740
We welcome mining enterprises

266
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:41,580
to participate in cooperative development.

267
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:43,200
We sincerely invite research institutions

268
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,960
to overcome the technical difficulties

269
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:47,000
of mining in the plateau permafrost areas.

270
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:49,510
We earnestly request our friends
in the media

271
00:12:49,510 --> 00:12:50,370
to objectively record

272
00:12:50,370 --> 00:12:52,370
the course of western development.

273
00:12:54,710 --> 00:12:55,910
Sorry, County Mayor.

274
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:57,920
My car broke down on the way.

275
00:12:58,300 --> 00:12:58,990
Sorry about that.

276
00:12:58,990 --> 00:12:59,580
I'm late.

277
00:13:00,930 --> 00:13:02,080
Comrades of the press,

278
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,280
