279
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:04,060
This is

280
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:05,770
the Mazhi County Party
Standing Committee member,

281
00:13:05,770 --> 00:13:06,870
Deputy County Mayor,

282
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:08,880
General Manager of

283
00:13:08,910 --> 00:13:09,820
Mazhi Economic Development Company,

284
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:11,440
and Bolamula Mountain Patrol's

285
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:12,300
person in charge,

286
00:13:12,300 --> 00:13:13,230
Comrade Duojie.

287
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:18,410
Sit down.

288
00:13:19,530 --> 00:13:20,790
Everyone, please sit.

289
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:26,940
Sorry, County Mayor.

290
00:13:26,940 --> 00:13:27,530
I interrupted you.

291
00:13:27,530 --> 00:13:28,010
No.

292
00:13:28,070 --> 00:13:29,070
Please continue.

293
00:13:29,770 --> 00:13:30,360
I've pretty much covered

294
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,760
the economic situation.

295
00:13:33,130 --> 00:13:34,390
Comrades of the press,

296
00:13:34,870 --> 00:13:36,540
to ensure the safety

297
00:13:36,570 --> 00:13:38,340
of people's lives and property,

